"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"![](https://miro.medium.com/max/1400/1\\\\*u8BzrRA6-i06X3-3bOkI_g.png)\\n\\n## “WePiggy’s Billionaires” on Moonriver\\n\\nIn order to encourage users to participate in WePiggy-Moonriver lending protocol, the WePiggy-Moonriver “WePiggy’s Billionaires” activity is now open!\\n\\n**Activity time:**2021/12/9 15:00 (UTC+8) to WePiggy’s official launch on the next public chain or layer 2 network\\n\\n**Activity Rules:**\\n\\nDuring the activity, participate in WePiggy-Moonriver WPC mining campaign, and the cumulative amount of mined WPC tokens ranks in the top **198** of the “WePiggy’s Billionaires”, will win the \\\\[ Moonriver Exclusive Edition\\\\] \\\\[Epic Level\\\\] NFT — “**ShadowPiggy**”.\\n\\n**Please note:**\\n\\n1\\\\. The “**ShadowPiggy**” NFT will be open for claim after the activity ends. Except for participating in this activity, or through the transfer of old holders in the future, no more “**ShadowPiggy**” will be generated.\\n\\n2\\\\. WePiggy reserves the right of final interpretation of this activity.\\n\\n## Activity Participation Tutorial\\n\\n[https://www.yuque.com/zgryhn/yboxrg/ri093u](https://www.yuque.com/zgryhn/yboxrg/ri093u)\\n\\n## About “ShadowPiggy” NFT\\n\\nThis card is issued to commemorate the 7th step of WePiggy’s cross-chain deployment plan: Moonriver.\\n\\nMoon in the river, like flowers in the mirror, to bring light to the world, she dares to be the first of the sister parachain DeFi ecosystem. Holder of this NFT will be blessed by WePiggy with the buff of “Moonlight Shadow, Moving Fast Forward”.\\n\\n## Join the community\\n\\nWebsite: [https://wepiggy.com](https://wepiggy.com/)\\n\\nTwitter: <https://twitter.com/wepiggydotcom>\\n\\nMedium: [https://wepiggy-com.medium.com](https://wepiggy-com.medium.com/)\\n\\nTelegram: <https://t.me/wepiggy>\\n\\nForum: [https://gov.wepiggy.com](https://gov.wepiggy.com/)\\n\\nDiscord: <https://discord.gg/wepiggy>\\n\\nGithub: <https://github.com/WePiggy>\",\"timestamp\":163